1
00:01:05,796 --> 00:01:08,228
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,356 --> 00:01:11,268
=Episode 21=

3
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:14,359
Are you feeling better?

4
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:17,640
You're not the one I saved.

5
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:20,439
You don't have to come here.

6
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:27,968
Virtuous Consort.

7
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:31,040
Are you mad at me about something?

8
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,159
No, I'm not.

9
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:36,400
I haven't yet recovered.
So I'm unable to serve you now.

10
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:39,120
If Your Majesty is displeased,
please leave.

11
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,400
(Zhao Qiluo still thinks Xu Yu is me.)

12
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:44,640
(That's why she treats me so coldly.)

13
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,400
Your Majesty.

14
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:53,280
Why are you standing so far from me?

15
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:55,319
Come closer.

16
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,120
Come on.

17
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:01,879
You keep her company.

18
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,640
She doesn't want me around now.

19
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:12,680
Your Majesty.

20
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,639
You've finally come to see me.

21
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,360
I was terrified!

22
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,919
The physician said you suffered a shock.

23
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,319
You're out of danger,

24
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:22,000
but you still need to rest for a while.

25
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,879
(His Majesty actually
shows concern for me!)

26
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,680
(Taking that stab is worth it.)

27
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,599
His Majesty just told me

28
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,080
that to thank you for saving me,

29
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,840
he intends to restore your title.

30
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,680
Really?

31
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,159
Your Majesty.

32
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,120
I really appreciate it.

33
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,280
I'll be even more dedicated than before!

34
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,479
Your Majesty.

35
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:55,120
(Zhao Qiluo mistakes me
for His Majesty,)

36
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,768
(becoming increasingly nice to me.)

37
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,200
(I cannot imagine
what she might do later.)

38
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:01,560
(How do I explain to her?)

39
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

40
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,280
Greetings, Your Majesty.

41
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,520
Why are you here?

42
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:17,439
I just left the Imperial Hospital.

43
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:20,759
I was deeply concerned for Your Majesty,
so I waited here for you.

44
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,159
Didn't you go see Jiang Tang?

45
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,879
His bandaging and treatment should have

46
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:33,639
prevented the wound from reopening.

47
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,240
The assassination attempt

48
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,159
overwhelmed physicians.

49
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:40,199
I didn't want to trouble them,
so I dressed the wound myself.

50
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:44,599
In that case, you should return home
to tend to your wound.

51
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,120
Thankfully, you saved me.

52
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:50,039
Later, I'll have the best medicine sent
to your residence.

53
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:57,120
Your Majesty,

54
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:00,960
do you recall that we once met briefly?

55
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:09,199
It was just a fleeting encounter.

56
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:11,240
It's understandable if you don't.

57
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:13,719
I'm leaving.

58
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,520
(Five years ago)

59
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,040
Sorry,

60
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,519
but I enjoy meddling.

61
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:45,600
(Xu Yu, it turns out
that a matter of life and death for me,)

62
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,240
(in your heart,)

63
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:55,120
(means nothing to you.)

64
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:01,439
Haven't you found anything wrong,
Your Highness?

65
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,040
What do you mean?

66
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:07,639
Their Majesties seem
to have switched back.

67
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,360
What?

68
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:12,600
Actually, during the banquet
for Queen of Dada,

69
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:16,160
and when Her Majesty had her arm
around Queen of Dada's shoulders,

70
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,120
I started to suspect something.

71
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,759
But seeing you enthusiastically trying
to please her,

72
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:23,759
I didn't dare tell you the truth.

73
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:25,879
So...

74
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:31,000
All this time
I've been buttering her up,

75
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,160
even throwing myself
in front of a blade.

76
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:36,560
It turns out I actually pleased Xu Yu!

77
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,560
Your Highness.

78
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,560
Your Highness.

79
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,079
You've worked hard

80
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:48,519
by staying undercover beside Xiao Jinle.

81
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,399
Have you uncovered anything?

82
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,360
Your Majesty,

83
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,160
the poison taken by the assassin
originated from Dada.

84
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,439
It's called Black Mist.

85
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,439
Dada again.

86
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:01,120
But Huna wouldn't harm Xu Yu.

87
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,920
Something may happen?

88
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,959
On the day Huna left, she met
with Xiao Jinle outside the city.

89
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:08,839
But the assassination attempt
is unrelated to Xiao Jinle.

90
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:12,399
The assassin was an imposter,
a dead agent of Prince Ning.

91
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,480
I just don't know
why Prince Ning would take such a risk.

92
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,800
It's because he
and his son are estranged

93
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,680
and starting to make foolish mistakes.

94
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,519
Do they suspect you?

95
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,439
No.

96
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,000
Prince Ning and his son are cautious.

97
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,839
They never rely on just one person.

98
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:32,399
Other dead agents
handle certain matters.

99
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:35,399
And Lady Tao is indeed,
as Your Majesty suspected,

100
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:37,160
associated with Xiao Jinle.

101
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,319
But sometimes, I can't even guess

102
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,920
what Prince Ning and his son truly want.

103
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:44,360
They won't be able to pretend
much longer.

104
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,199
Keep a watch on them.

105
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,439
I want to find out

106
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:51,000
if the other uncles are on their side.

107
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,300
Yes.

108
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:55,360
How did you get the Black Mist?

109
00:06:56,360 --> 00:07:00,040
Every soldier under your command
obeys my orders.

110
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:03,839
You thought that Dada's shaman Abudu,
having cooperated with you for years,

111
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,040
would follow your lead.

112
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:08,800
But now, he seems to trust me more.

113
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:11,279
Once Xu Yu is executed
after her pregnancy,

114
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,319
I can rally other officials

115
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:16,720
to propose you as crown prince,
citing Xiao Jinyun's lack of heirs.

116
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,279
But you...

117
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:19,000
You should be grateful Xu Yu didn't die.

118
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:22,360
Otherwise, your mansion
would run red with blood tonight.

119
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,439
I wouldn't want this dreadful poison

120
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,639
forced down your throat, Father.

121
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,120
If it comes to that,

122
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:38,920
I'll fulfill my filial duty
and join you in your grave.

123
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:40,439
I do all this for you.

124
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:41,920
You're doing it for yourself.

125
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:45,279
And I'm no different.

126
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:49,160
Xu Yu merely helped you out once
when you were young.

127
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,199
Why do you value her so much?

128
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,680
Remember
how your grandfather's family died?

129
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,120
Your mother still lives
in that nightmare.

130
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,519
Xiao Jinyun's father is to blame.

131
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:59,079
His son should pay the price.

132
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,800
I remember that.

133
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,759
But the one
who deserves to die is Xiao Jinyun.

134
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,680
Laying a hand on Xu Yu is unacceptable.

135
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:11,639
It's a pity

136
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,879
I always have a backup plan.

137
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,279
You stopped one,

138
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,360
but you

139
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,639
can't stop the other.

140
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:21,120
Only when Xu Yu is dead

141
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:24,279
can we sever Xiao Jinyun's ties
to the Xu family.

142
00:08:24,459 --> 00:08:24,959
You...

143
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:27,920
Your plan in the capital
will be more secure.

144
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,000
Xiao Jinle.

145
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:34,039
Isn't chaos exactly what you want?

146
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,960
How unpredictable life is.

147
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,679
Now,

148
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,759
this palace is truly full of dangers.

149
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:01,039
Royal families are the most heartless.

150
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:03,480
It always happens.

151
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,919
You seem quite optimistic.

152
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,559
If I didn't,

153
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,240
life would be even harder.

154
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:13,879
Thinking back to
when I was crowned the Empress,

155
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,159
Your Majesty never treated me kindly.

156
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:21,559
I thought we'd be at odds forever.

157
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:26,519
Xu Yu.

158
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,399
But things have changed.

159
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:32,919
Yes, of course.

160
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,159
Before, I always felt stifled
in the palace.

161
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:39,639
Now, even Consort Zhao
is friendly toward me,

162
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:43,799
though she's only being nice
because she learned about our body swap.

163
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:47,039
After the assassination attempt,

164
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:49,200
Lady Liang secretly told me

165
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,440
that she has already known
we've switched back.

166
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,080
She was furious.

167
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:56,440
But she never regretted saving me.

168
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,879
She has admirable qualities.

169
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,960
So I think

170
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:05,039
I could become good friends

171
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,240
with Consort Zhao.

172
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:09,519
This palace

173
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,080
has trapped too many people.

174
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:13,320
Xu Yu,

175
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,159
you should have been as free as a bird,

176
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,519
soaring in the skies.

177
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,879
Now, confined within the walls,

178
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,679
as my Empress,

179
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,559
do you ever regret it?

180
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,080
A weary bird will return to its nest.

181
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,720
A wanderer seeks his home.

182
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,000
Xiao Jinyun,

183
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,399
you are my safe haven.

184
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:40,240
We're never to be separated.

185
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,080
without doubts about each other.

186
00:10:44,444 --> 00:10:47,765
♪As if yesterday left no regrets♪

187
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:51,360
As husband and wife,

188
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,960
we have no doubts about each other.

189
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,840
I think this tastes better.

190
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,360
Is it sour?

191
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:12,720
But lately, I've been craving sour food.

192
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:15,559
I've heard

193
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,919
it's a sign of having a boy.

194
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,039
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

195
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:28,600
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

196
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,440
Empress Dowager sent these
along with other gifts.

197
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:35,000
She said placing the infant clothes
of robust elders

198
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,159
under your pillow

199
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:37,960
ensures a strong and healthy child.

200
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,799
I never heard of it.

201
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,720
Bring them up.

202
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,879
The one with rabbits
is from Prince Xiaoyao.

203
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:46,919
The one with tigers
is from Prince Ning's son.

204
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,320
Keep Jinming's.

205
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,000
Put away the one from Xiao Jinle.

206
00:11:54,039 --> 00:11:54,559
Yes.

207
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:03,679
Jinming has been working
with your brother on flood relief.

208
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:05,000
He hasn't slept for days.

209
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:07,039
Prince Ning even created obstacles.

210
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:09,600
Xu Yu.

211
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,840
Once I root out his faction,

212
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,639
we'll travel to the desert again

213
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,840
to relax a bit.

214
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,559
It won't be long now.

215
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:20,919
The more capable you prove,
the more anxious they become.

216
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:23,240
They'll make another risky move.

217
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,519
Xu Yu, what's wrong?

218
00:12:44,559 --> 00:12:45,059
Xu Yu!

219
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:47,919
Xu Yu!

220
00:13:04,992 --> 00:13:10,176
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

221
00:13:10,912 --> 00:13:15,475
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

222
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:22,215
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

223
00:13:22,784 --> 00:13:27,328
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

224
00:13:27,968 --> 00:13:33,232
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

225
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:39,277
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

226
00:13:39,616 --> 00:13:41,632
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

227
00:13:41,824 --> 00:13:45,568
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

228
00:13:46,144 --> 00:13:50,816
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

229
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,120
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

230
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:57,056
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

231
00:13:57,303 --> 00:14:02,830
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
